title: Acorn Icons BETA v1.0.0
description:
Welcome to a new experience. Acorn is a unique, colourful and shapeless icon pack.

It's still in beta so there's just 250 icons at the moment, but there's plenty more to come. So please do be patient. There's also 8 awesome wallpapers to make your setups look awesome ;)

Also, remember to use the icon request tool to send in your un-themed icons. The waiting time at the moment is just 1 week!

My future plans for acorn include

- A new app icon
- Get to 800 icons by July
- Dashboard tweaks/fixes

More info:
 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.skykonig.acornicons
